  "detailed_description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>ESC (Electronics Security Company)</strong> is a hacking game that challenges players to step into the shoes of an \"ethical\" hacker. As an infiltrator, you are entrusted with hacking into various computer systems to accomplish  objectives and unveil hidden secrets. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2811590/extras/6512e47870c89146f763ac7df26e03b3.poster.avif?t=1766570043\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2811590/extras/6512e47870c89146f763ac7df26e03b3.webm?t=1766570043\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2811590/extras/6512e47870c89146f763ac7df26e03b3.mp4?t=1766570043\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >you must strategically navigate through a diverse range of scenarios, each presenting unique challenges and objectives. Work through a variety of missions as you infiltrate systems to unravel hidden secrets and retrieve sensitive information.  </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2811590/extras/6a8c0d5939b3c2f226e2965ad56da85e.poster.avif?t=1766570043\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2811590/extras/6a8c0d5939b3c2f226e2965ad56da85e.webm?t=1766570043\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2811590/extras/6a8c0d5939b3c2f226e2965ad56da85e.mp4?t=1766570043\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Objectives vary from task to task. You can tackle them at your own pace while exploring your own machine and others.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2811590/extras/03f2c1df9cd37c26acb4e3ddf7142506.poster.avif?t=1766570043\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2811590/extras/03f2c1df9cd37c26acb4e3ddf7142506.webm?t=1766570043\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2811590/extras/03f2c1df9cd37c26acb4e3ddf7142506.mp4?t=1766570043\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Challenge your skills as you hack and explore devices,  and uncover the secrets behind ESC.</p>",
  "about_the_game": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>ESC (Electronics Security Company)</strong> is a hacking game that challenges players to step into the shoes of an \"ethical\" hacker. As an infiltrator, you are entrusted with hacking into various computer systems to accomplish  objectives and unveil hidden secrets. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2811590/extras/6512e47870c89146f763ac7df26e03b3.poster.avif?t=1766570043\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2811590/extras/6512e47870c89146f763ac7df26e03b3.webm?t=1766570043\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2811590/extras/6512e47870c89146f763ac7df26e03b3.mp4?t=1766570043\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >you must strategically navigate through a diverse range of scenarios, each presenting unique challenges and objectives. Work through a variety of missions as you infiltrate systems to unravel hidden secrets and retrieve sensitive information.  </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2811590/extras/6a8c0d5939b3c2f226e2965ad56da85e.poster.avif?t=1766570043\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2811590/extras/6a8c0d5939b3c2f226e2965ad56da85e.webm?t=1766570043\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2811590/extras/6a8c0d5939b3c2f226e2965ad56da85e.mp4?t=1766570043\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Objectives vary from task to task. You can tackle them at your own pace while exploring your own machine and others.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2811590/extras/03f2c1df9cd37c26acb4e3ddf7142506.poster.avif?t=1766570043\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2811590/extras/03f2c1df9cd37c26acb4e3ddf7142506.webm?t=1766570043\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2811590/extras/03f2c1df9cd37c26acb4e3ddf7142506.mp4?t=1766570043\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Challenge your skills as you hack and explore devices,  and uncover the secrets behind ESC.</p>",
